<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: 0;
            font-size: 100%;
        }
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .sidebar {
            flex-basis: 20%;
            color: #fff;
            padding-top: 20px;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: #333;
        }
        p{
            font-size: 30px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }
        .mainpage {
            flex-basis: 80%;
            border: 1px solid darkgreen;
            padding: 1rem;

        }
        .store_title{
            border-bottom: 1px solid black;
            width: 1000px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .store_sub{
            background-color: orange;
            width: 1000px;
            height: 30px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }
        #btn_store{
            width: 200px;
            height: 30px;
            font-size: large;
            background-color: orange;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-left: 50px;

        }
        .menu1{
            /* border: 1px solid black; */
            margin-left: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 1000px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        .image h2{
            text-align:left;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 30px;
        }

        h5 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            list-style: none;
        }

        ul li a {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        ul li a:hover {
            color: white;
        }
       #btn_cancel, #btn_list{
            width: 500px;
            height: 40px;
            font-size: large;
            background-color: orange;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .finish_space{
            margin-left: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<form>
    <main class="container">
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <p>사장님 페이지</p>
            <h5> > 가게 정보</h5>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><a href="StoreAdd.mustache">가게 등록</a></li>
                <li><a href="StoreEdit.mustache">가게 수정</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">리뷰 관리</a></li>
            </ul>
            <h5> > 매출 관리</h5>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><a href="#">오늘의 매출</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">월 매출</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">년 매출</a></li>
            </ul>
            <h5> > 예약 관리</h5>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><a href="#">이번 주 예약</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">지난 예약</a></li>
            </ul>
            <h5> > 공지 사항</h5>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><a href="#">공지사항</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">서비스 소개</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">자주 묻는 질문</a></li>
            </ul>
        </aside>
        <section class="mainpage" style="overflow-y: scroll;">
            <fieldset>
                <div>
                    <br>
                    <p>  > 가게</p></div><br>
                <div class="store_title">
                    가게 상세보기 페이지 입니다.
                </div><br>
                <div class="store_sub">
                    <button id="btn_store">가게조회</button>
                    <button id="btn_store">가게등록</button>
                    <button id="btn_store">가게수정</button>
                </div><br>
                <table class="table">
                    <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="col">번호</th>
                        <th scope="col">이름</th>
                        <th scope="col">연락처</th>
                        <th scope="col">주소</th>
                        <th scope="col">오픈시간</th>
                        <th scope="col">마감시간</th>
                        <th scope="col">휴무일</th>
                        <th scope="col">가게설명</th>
                        <th scope="col">가게사진</th>
                    </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                    {{#store}}
                        <tr>
                            <th>{{id}}</th>
                            <th>{{name}}</th>
                            <td>{{phone}}</td>
                            <td>{{address}}</td>
                            <td>{{open_time}}</td>
                            <td>{{close_time}}</td>
                            <td>{{rest_day}}</td>
                            <td>{{content}}</td>
                            <td>{{photo}}</td>
                        </tr>
                    {{/store}}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <div class="finish_space">
                <a href="/store/{{id}}/delete" >삭제하기</a>
                <button id="btn_list"><a href="/store" >목록가기</a></button>
                </div>
            </fieldset>
        </section>
    </main>
</form>
</body>
</html>